            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the veg is in the oven, combine the <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and <strong>goats' cheese</strong> and whisk together until fairly smooth</p><p>Add a grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>whipped goats' cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1595941550625-x200.jpg",
