            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, cut the <strong>plain naans</strong> in half on the diagonal, then add them to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 3 min or until the bread is hot – these are your <strong>chilli naans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1595941556349-x200.jpg",
